4 output formats\"}],\" — MP4 (H.264), WebM (VP8), AVI (MPEG-4), and GIF cover web, mobile, legacy, and social media needs.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Video to GIF\"}],\" — Two-pass GIF conversion with per-frame palette optimization. Capped at 12 fps and 720p for reasonable file sizes.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Batch conversion\"}],\" — Add multiple files and convert them all to the same format sequentially.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Optimal codecs\"}],\" — Each format uses its best codec automatically: H.264 for MP4, VP8 for WebM, MPEG-4 for AVI.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"100% client-side\"}],\" — Uses ffmpeg.wasm (WebAssembly). Your videos never leave your device.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"How to Convert Video Files\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"1. Add videos\"}],\" — Drag and drop video files into the upload area, or click to browse. Supports MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, MKV.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"2. Choose format\"}],\" — Select your target format: MP4, WebM, AVI, or GIF.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"3. Convert\"}],\" — Click Convert and wait for processing. Each file shows its own progress bar.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"4. Download\"}],\" — Click the download icon next to each file, or use Download All to grab everything.\"]}]]}],[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Video Converter\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Pick the container based on where the video is going\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Pick the container based on where the video is going\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"MP4 (H.264) is the safest bet for messaging, social, and most players. WebM works on every modern browser and is smaller. MOV is for Apple-specific workflows. MKV is for archive and remuxing.\"}]]}]]}],\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\",\"$L2e\"]}]]}],\"$L2f\",\"$L30\"],\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\"]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/0t6pan-62f3ah.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n23:[\"$\",\"$L35\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$28\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@36\"}]}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Match output bitrate to source quality\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$21:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Match output bitrate to source quality\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Up-encoding a 2 Mbps source to 10 Mbps doesn't recover quality — it just inflates the file. Pick a bitrate near the source's average for like-for-like quality.\"}]]}]]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Use H.265 (HEVC) only when target supports it\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$21:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Use H.265 (HEVC) only when target supports it\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"HEVC saves 30–50% bytes vs H.264 at the same quality, but some browsers and older devices can't play it. For broad compatibility, stick to H.264 inside MP4.\"}]]}]]}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Keep the source frame rate\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$21:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Keep the source frame rate\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Converting 60 fps source to 30 fps drops half the frames and makes motion look choppy. Convert frame rate only when a target platform explicitly requires it.\"}]]}]]}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Re-encoding when remuxing would work\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\",\"key\":\"wmoenq\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 9v4\",\"key\":\"juzpu7\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 17h.01\",\"key\":\"p32p05\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Re-encoding when remuxing would work\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"If you only need to change containers (MKV → MP4) and the codecs inside are already compatible, stream-copy remuxing is instant and lossless. Full re-encoding is slow and lossy.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Choosing a high bitrate for a short clip on a slow connection\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2f:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Choosing a high bitrate for a short clip on a slow connection\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"I